data.description: Rare opportunity to add your personal touches to this spacious and bright 3-bed, 2-bath split level home in the heart of Naperville!  This home offers a sun-filled living room with hardwood flooring, a formal dining area, an eat-in kitchen with ample storage and sliding doors to the back yard, large bedrooms, 2 full baths, a lower level family room, and attached 2-car garage.  Sold as-is.  No survey.  This is a must see.  Schedule a showing today!
